ActCanadian Dairy Commission Act
PrecisReappointment of SERGE RIENDEAU of Coaticook, Quebec, as Chief Executive Officer of the Canadian Dairy Commission, to hold office during pleasure for a term ending on June 30, 2022, or until such time as a new Chief Executive Officer is appointed, whichever occurs first, effective May 14, 2022.
